wiki.summary: In “pushin P,” Gunna, Future and Young Thug come together for a catchy trap song where the artists rap about drugs, women, money, and jewelry. Gunna first previewed the track’s music video on his Instagram, on December 29, 2021. Just five days prior to the audio’s release, on January 12, 2022, Gunna released the official music video which was directed by Caleb Jermale. Read more on Last.fm.
